<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ | My MCP Shelf</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Frequently asked questions about Model Context Protocol, MCP servers, and how to use My MCP Shelf">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.mymcpshelf.com/faq/" />
